        {
            "title": "歐洲股市下跌 投資者等待美伊潛在和平談判相關消息",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 歐洲股市下跌，在霍爾木茲海峽對峙持續之際，投資者密切關注美伊潛在和平談判的進展。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">斯托克歐洲600指數收跌。科技股和能源股跑贏，醫療健保、汽車和礦業股則表現最為滯後。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該歐洲基準股指收窄一度達1%的跌幅，巴基斯坦官員宣布伊朗外長阿巴斯·阿拉格齊預計將於周五晚間抵達伊斯蘭堡，可能與美國舉行第二輪和平談判後，布倫特原油從每桶107美元跌至104美元。伊朗半官方的塔斯尼姆通訊社報導稱，阿拉格齊此行不安排與美國進行會談。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9a3c26b9-62f4-3b39-a775-a2f236452561-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中東衝突的長期僵局給歐洲股市帶來了沉重壓力，使其失去了今年早些時候相較於美國股市的優異表現，投資者擔心高油價會影響經濟成長。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">斯托克歐洲600指數年初至今的漲幅已縮減至，落後於標普500指數的漲幅。人工智能驅動的科技股盈利勢頭也支撐了美股。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kfv.PueO87DKVY_qLIls3w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/6639b50119dd6ae9c5d9c6d81ddc14ad\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">巴黎La Financiere de l’Echiquier交易主管David Kruk表示，「本財報季的一個重要結論是，美國重回領先地位，這主要歸功於其在科技和半導體領域的統治地位。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲企業財報方面，德國的SAP走高，提振了該地區的科技板塊。這家軟件公司發布的雲訂單積壓成長安撫了投資者對人工智能擾動的擔憂。在公佈第一季度業績後，被視為能源基礎設施和人工智能數據中心需求激增主要受益者的西門子能源上漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題European Stocks Fall as Investors Await Word of Iran Peace Talks</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Levin Stamm、Michael Msika.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
