        {
            "title": "Google與Anthropic深化合作:400億美元交易為基礎設施建設鋪路",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Nvib4xSMzsyQIvZwgu7Dkw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEAAG092_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - Alphabet Inc. (NASDAQ:GOOGL) 股價週五盤中攀升,上漲1.2%,此前彭博社報導稱Google計劃向<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Anthropic\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Anthropic;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Anthropic\">Anthropic</a>投資高達400億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據報導,Google將向Anthropic PBC投資100億美元,並可能追加300億美元。這筆交易加強了兩家公司之間的關係,它們既是人工智能開發領域的合作夥伴,也是競爭對手。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Anthropic表示,Google承諾以3,500億美元的估值投資100億美元現金,該估值與2月份融資輪的估值相同。這家Alphabet旗下的公司將在Anthropic達成績效目標後再投資300億美元,並支持Anthropic大幅擴展其運算能力。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3c4d3e9d-0a96-344e-82de-854086557be0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在Claude Code取得成功後,這家初創公司加快了融資步伐。Claude Code是一款能夠加速編寫電腦軟體過程的AI代理工具。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/google%E8%88%87anthropic%E6%B7%B1%E5%8C%96%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-400%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E7%82%BA%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%BD%E5%BB%BA%E8%A8%AD%E9%8B%AA%E8%B7%AF-170733772.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-25 01:10:12",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "TD Cowen生成式AI採用調查看好這些股票",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.130ucTWhmOBTs8AJXOEJw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA9Q076_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - TD <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Cowen\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Cowen;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Cowen\">Cowen</a>分析師Derrick Wood主導的一項最新調查報告顯示,人工智能貨幣化正接近拐點,現有軟體供應商的受益程度將超過市場目前的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司針對生產力套件市場發布的第三份報告,基於對689名美國採購決策者的調查,發現生成式AI的採用已相當普遍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據Wood表示,92%的受訪者至少使用三大供應商之一,包括微軟Copilot(70%)、谷歌Gemini(55%)和OpenAI的ChatGPT(53%),而企業平均部署2.6家AI代理供應商。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2967d639-5a63-3203-998b-b4ad246e41f1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管採用率很高,但貨幣化程度仍然較低。不過TD Cowen預計這種情況將會改變,75%的受訪者表示AI代理帶來了正面的投資回報率,79%的<span><span><span><span>微軟</span></span></span></span> 365用戶和80%的Google Workspace用戶表示,他們在未來12至18個月內有些可能或非常可能升級其套件訂閱。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該報告對企業SaaS供應商特別看好。Wood寫道,這些數據「描繪出比目前股價所反映的更有利的AI貨幣化前景,尤其是對企業SaaS供應商而言。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">TD Cowen指出Salesforce、ServiceNow和SAP為主要受益者,並指出儘管橫向AI代理目前採用率最低,但其感知投資回報率最高,58%的用戶表示獲得3倍或更高的回報。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自主AI的採用也將大幅加速,TD Cowen預計部署率將從目前的34%增加一倍以上,到2027年下半年達到77%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">具體針對微軟,TD Cowen將其Microsoft 365商業收入的複合年增長率預測從約13.5%上調至15%(至2030財年),目前預計收入將達到1,056億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/td-cowen%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E5%BC%8Fai%E6%8E%A1%E7%94%A8%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E5%A5%BD%E9%80%99%E4%BA%9B%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8-155115726.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-25 00:02:48",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "英偉達搶走英特爾風頭:5萬億美元巨頭飆升,AI市場轉向CPU",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DkDpYjpDmIaIJWpMGtgkUQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA8400B_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"英偉達\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:英偉達;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/英偉達\">英偉達</a>(NASDAQ:NVDA)股價週五上漲5%,此前英特爾公佈強勁財報,提振整個半導體板塊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英特爾第一季度業績顯示,來自AI服務供應商的中央處理器需求超出預期,該公司甚至售出了此前已註銷的晶片。<span><span><span><span>英特爾</span></span></span></span>股價飆升24%至83美元,推動其市值突破4,160億美元,超越2000年互聯網泡沫時期的峰值。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">漲勢蔓延至整個晶片板塊,AMD上漲14%,Arm上漲超過13%。這些漲幅反映出市場日益堅信,推理——即AI系統回答用戶查詢的過程——可能讓中央處理器恢復更重要的地位,此前多年來圖形晶片一直主導AI訓練工作負載。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3c958c06-783c-3b9a-a3a9-dc3796880fea-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英偉達5萬億美元的市值使其成為週五以美元計算的最大推動力量。值得注意的是,英偉達上月推出了新的中央處理器,標誌著其罕見地擴張至傳統上由英特爾和<span><span>AMD</span></span>主導的領域。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司於2023年推出Grace CPU,這是一款基於ARM架構的處理器,旨在與其GPU協同工作於Grace Hopper和Grace Blackwell超級晶片中,以減少AI工作負載中的數據瓶頸。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在GTC 2026上,英偉達推出了採用定制Olympus核心和空間多線程技術的Vera CPU,該公司表示,對於代理AI任務,其效率是傳統x86 CPU的兩倍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%B1%E5%81%89%E9%81%94%E6%90%B6%E8%B5%B0%E8%8B%B1%E7%89%B9%E7%88%BE%E9%A2%A8%E9%A0%AD-5%E8%90%AC%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%B7%A8%E9%A0%AD%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87-ai%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E8%BD%89%E5%90%91cpu-164333484.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-25 01:10:14",
